<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>: <span class="c2">(رَصَنَهُ)</span> يَرْصنُه رَصْناً: <span class="c2">(أَكْمَلَهُ)</span> ، نَقَلَهُ الجَوْهرِيُّ عَن الأصْمعيّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> رَصَنَه <span class="c2">(بِلِسانِه)</span> رَصْناً: (شَتَمهُ وأَرْصَنَه: أَحْكَمَه كَمَا فِي<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>